@@TJvCustomAppXMLStorage.CreateAndSetNode
Summary
  Creates the indicated node and sets FCurrentNode
Description
  Reads the \ separated Key string and sets FCurrentNode to the last one, having created all the
  required XML nodes including the last one
Parameters
  Key - The key to create
See Also
  FCurrentNode


